    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"/>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">This concept only concerns the organisational management of rights, and does not represent the rights themselves - especially where such 'rights' are legally recognised or defined for the data subject or individual. The concept dpv:DataSubjectRight is provided to represent such legal rights.</skos:scopeNote>
