    <dct:contributor>Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Beatriz Esteves</dct:contributor>
    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Right Non-Fulfilment Notice</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">This notice is associated with situations where information is provided with the intention of communicating non-fulfilment of a right. For example, to provide justifications on why a right could not be fulfilled or providing information about another entity  who should be approached for exercising this right.</skos:scopeNote>
