  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/dpv/owl#RegulatorySandbox">
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Mechanism used by regulators and businesses for gauging the compatibility of regulations and innovative products, particularly in the context of digitalisation, in a controlled real-world environment with appropriate safeguards in place</skos:definition>
